      <head>Ferdinand Avenarius</head>
      <div>

        <p>German poet, author of many books, founding editor of the influential journal <ref
            cRef="entity-003014"><title level="j">Der Kunstwart</title></ref> from 1887 to his death
          in 1923. He was a lyric poet and a leading representative of the culture reform movement
          of his time and the first popularizer of the Sylt area of northern Germany.</p>
      </div>
